Package: apparmor.d
Architecture: any
Depends: apparmor-profiles, ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: apparmor-profiles-extra, apparmor.d.enforced,
Description: Full set of AppArmor profiles (complain mode)
 apparmor.d is a set of over 2000 AppArmor policies whose aim is to confine
 most Linux based applications and processes.

